{
  "stem": "11744.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was mainly involved with a very famous shoe concern called Bata, which is from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he-- he introduced it in Western Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he finally he finally opened a big factory in eastern France, and employed 2,000 workers, and manufacturing in France instead of-- instead of importing from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was a fine champion of fencing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a Vice President of the Fencing Federation of France-- and fencing was always the big thing in my household.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother did fencing, I did fencing, and we sometimes did it together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were very much involved in that, because my father was very involved.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was no more-- there was no more activity, illegal activity, going on, I mean, when everything was normal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After all, life was normal until the war broke out in 1939.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my husband's grandfather was chief rabbi of Paris, so we had pretty good exposure.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was the first-- I was the very first student at the reform temple that was opened when I was about 12.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was the first student to attend this school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we only had one reform temple in Paris and it was never recognized as legal by the-- by the organization-- which is called the Consistoire.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Consistoire is the-- the-- well, that's-- it's an organization that all the temple belonged to, and they're the ones who nominate rabbis for different city in France, and-- and for Paris, of course.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And every temple belongs, every synagogue belonged, but the reform temple never did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They never accepted it, and it was never considered legal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It had the name of the-- of the street in which it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was Temple Copernic, because the street was Copernic.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
